{{#IF_ISSUES}}## Two Workflows, Same Outcome

```
Slack "Fix This" → Linear ticket (agent-ready) → Slot implements → /ship → PR → Merge
/advisor plan    → /dispatch → Linear ticket    → Slot implements → /ship → PR → Merge
```

Both converge on Linear tickets. `agent-ready` label is the universal dispatch mechanism.

